	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Version 0.25</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Changelog:
<br />0.25
<br />Implemented Hard Reset (F11 key) and Soft Reset (F12 key).
<br />Implemented switch from PAL system and NTSC with F8 Key.
<br />Implemented PPU Open Bus and correct some bugs in DMC emulation.
<br />Implemented AxROM, BxROM, GxROM and CPROM mappers.
<br />I finally manage to pass all the Blargg's tests that I've found on the internet (including sprdma_and_dmc_dma.nes and sprdma_and_dmc_dma_512.nes).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


