	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Changelog:
<br />0.29 (bugfix release)
<br />correct some bugs and redesigned the timeline in the windows version.
<br />In the linux version i dropped the dependency with some libraries (such as the libpng 1.4) and this should make the emulator also run correctly on distributions like Ubuntu.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


