		<td><b>Version 0.30</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Changelog:
<br />0.30
<br />added a save/load state system with 6 slots.
<br />F1 = save state
<br />F2 = dec slot
<br />F3 = inc slot
<br />F4 = load state

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


