<br />0.32 (bugfix release)
<br />correct another bugs in the save system. I have tested many many roms and now everything (hopefully) works perfectly. Delete (for the last time [hopefully]) the directory "save" located in the folder "$HOME/.puNES" on linux or "&lt;Documents&gt;/puNES" on Windows.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
